Store your first name and last name in separate variables and print full name.

Create variable pi with value 3.14 and convert it to integer.

Create a variable and delete it. Try printing after deletion.

Assign integer value to a variable and later change it to string. Print both times.

Create variable with name _price and assign 500.

Check whether variable names 1num, num1, _num, num_one are valid.

Store result of (10+5)*2 in a variable and print it.

